reviewText: He has such an original spin on comedy that I felt priveldged to wittness his entire career unfold. This dvd is what his name says he is "The Entertainer" with all of the dancing and some singing and of course straight to the gut jokes!

This was a good standup for Cedric. He used a more mature approach with this one and it was still funny as ever. Cedric the Entertainer is one of the greatest comedians of our time. He ads a little dancing in there, and we all know he likes to dance. But all around it was a good show.

This is the funniest comedy stand-up i've seen in years! Cedric put it down on this one! I saw this on HBO like 5-6 times, after it quit running, I had to buy it. There is no one out there right now that's funnier than my dude Cedric the Entertainer!
Ceddy did his thing.  The ladies are hot - his performance is hotter.  My dad enjoyed it - it was part of a stocking stuffer for him at Christmas.
Shipping time was fast & precise.  DVD was new and played without flaw.  This DVD was hilarious and enjoyed it very much (I'm a fan of cedric the entertainer).

Cedric made a good comeback with this stand up routine. I mean this show is absolutely hilarious. Sort of reminds me of when he was on  def comedy jam. A wide variety of topics are discussed and made fun of in this show. Full of classic material from beginning to end. One of my favorites is Jerry rice on Dancing with the stars. A great addition to your dvd collection.
Funny just like all his other comedy dvd
Great dvd!  Very funny, he sings, dances, jokes!  I can see why he calls himself the entertainer!  Would definitely recommend it and wish he had a more current dvd.
My boyfriend and i LOVE to watch standups...and Cedric is one of the best.  If you like Cedric, you'll like this one.  Very entertaining!
Cedric will definitely entertain and you can tell he works hard to try and make sure you get your money's worth!
cedric pulls through in here for one of the king of comedy he doesnt fail at what he does and i love it great dvd great part of my comedy collection
This video is so hilarious. I was watchin it On Demand and I watched it EVERYDAY while home on maternity leave. When they took it off, I almost cried. I had to buy it. Its funnier every time.
I recommend this DVD to anyone is hilarious, is fun Cedric is a classic entertainer, I love it. I could stop laughing from the beginning to the end. Just buy it is worth it.
Ced is a total entertainment package!  Cute as heck, funny as sin, and can daaaance!  Yeah.  We love him.

I was thrilled to receive this DVD in time for the holidays, but was sorely disappointed at the condition of the disk. There were small chip marks all around the edge of the disk. I realize the risk of purchasing used items, the condition of the disk was worse than I expected.
Great Stand-Up, Great Price, Great Shipping... Would definitely recommend for Business to a Friend. A MUST Have!
